#  <%= current_page.data.title %>

[Sentry.io](https://sentry.io/) is an open-source full-stack error tracking system which supports a wide range of server, browser, desktop and native mobile languages and frameworks.

### Access
Request access from [Digital tools](<%= data.site.digital_tools %>).
Complete the Digital Tools Request Form at the top of the slack channel.

Or ask a Sentry Org Manager to add you to a team or project.

### New Project
To create a new project you need to raise a request with [Digital tools](<%= data.site.digital_tools %>), providing them with the plan type, and approval from your budget holder/DD.

You will need to know the approximate number of errors, transactions and attachments.

